metadata.description:
The Chuchu Cup is stakefish's special Valentine's edition item. There are only 200 cups. Use this item to decorate your favorite [RTFKT PodX](https://opensea.io/collection/rtfkt-podx) and [RTFKT Space Pod](https://opensea.io/collection/rtfkt-space-pod-4) with love.

Designed by [stakefish](https://stake.fish/), your friendly neighborhood validator.
https://twitter.com/stakefish
